> 
> set_rules <- function(x, heavy, light) {
+   # x: the character vector returned by etable
+ 
+   tex2add <- ""
+   if (!missing(heavy)) {
+     tex2add <- paste0("\\setlength\\heavyrulewidth{", heavy, "}\n")
+   }
+   if (!missing(light)) {
+     tex2add <- paste0(tex2add, "\\setlength\\lightrulewidth{", light, "}\n")
+   }
+ 
+   if (nchar(tex2add) > 0) {
+     x[x == "%start:tab\n"] <- tex2add
+   }
+ 
+   x
+ }
>
